{"type": "article", "id": 12386, "title": "Native Apollo Moc 白色款式", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-21T07:42:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 45, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607105806RPoquVZUeXcNy29g.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自加拿大温哥华的鞋履品牌 Native 最近为其经典鞋款 Apollo Moc 推出白色款式。这款鞋子因为使用了特殊的材料，整个鞋身只有 6 盎司的重量，再加上使用超细的纤维材质，有非常优秀的透气本领，而且全鞋身没有缝合的痕迹，听起来有点适合处女座呀。鞋子售价 70 美元，这是<a href=\"http://www.kicksonfire.com/tag/native/\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140139NV0oJtbvQiFjSusg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94211823\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140140DGMS6JLxk7iwX0Q9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00735294\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140140ZisT0n4J2hNCpyYO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00146843\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140141yUi1BHT0aQrkFXhL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67467249\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140141e3HjkZlPYnws182o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726140142x1kbNcJh3gO2fQmt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}